 # 🏦 Mini Bank Management System

A simple console-based **Bank Management System** written in **C++**.  
This project demonstrates **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)** concepts and **file handling** using binary files.

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Create new bank accounts
- ✅ Deposit money
- ✅ Withdraw money with minimum balance check
- ✅ Display account details
- ✅ Modify account information
- ✅ Close an account
- ✅ Display all account holders
- ✅ Data stored persistently using binary file (`account.dat`)

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- **Language:** C++
- **Concepts:** Classes, Encapsulation, File I/O (Binary Files), Menu-driven console app

---

